Class ResourceStridedSliceAssign

java.lang.Object
org.tensorflow.op.RawOp
org.tensorflow.op.core.ResourceStridedSliceAssign
All Implemented Interfaces:
Op
@Operator public final class ResourceStridedSliceAssign extends RawOp
Assign value to the sliced l-value reference of ref. The values of value are assigned to the positions in the variable ref that are selected by the slice parameters. The slice parameters begin, end, strides, etc. work exactly as in StridedSlice`.

NOTE this op currently does not support broadcasting and so value's shape must be exactly the shape produced by the slice of ref.
